{
  "arquivo": "ca03_21",
  "total": 90,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Has the sun already set?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "The day sure went by in a flash, didn't it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I want to keep playing,\\nbut it's time to head back right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, wait!\\nHow about we watch the sunset from here?\\nWe still have time for that, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Sounds good!\\nThere's a place called Emerald Beach,\\nlet's go check it out.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-san, Miku, are you guys okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sure, yeah.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I want to see the sunset too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Alright, let's head to Emerald Beach together!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Walking side by side with Futaro...\\n I can hardly believe it.\\n It almost feels like a dream.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku, you tired?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No, I'm fine.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "After all, it's Yotsuba and Raiha who are walking ahead.\\nThose two'll go faster and faster if no one warns them.\\nRemember to tell me if you can't keep up.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Thanks.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You're such a good boyfriend, Futaro-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "This kind of thing is usual.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, Fu-kun has always been really kind.\\nHe's just hard to read sometimes.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Nino's right. I thought I had understood\\n Futaro's kindness when it comes to\\n understanding people's feelings.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(I'm sorry, Futaro.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ichika, Nino,\\nplease don't interfere too much with them, okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Ah, okay then.\\nTake your time walking back.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "We'll be waiting at Emerald Beach.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Man, can't believe we're already getting scolded\\neven by Itsuki.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(I don't mind this kind of silence.\\n If it's with Futaro...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(...Huh?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro's...holding...my...HAND!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "F-Futaro...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(He looks unbothered...but his ears are bright red.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(If that's the case...\\n Maybe I'll squeeze his hand back,\\n just a little?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro's hand is bigger than I thought,\\n I feel a sense of relief when his hand wraps around mine.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Doing this makes me feel warm inside, somehow...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Huh? Wh-what's this?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Are we...interlocking our fingers...right now?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "F-Futaro...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh?!\\nN-no, nothing...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Th-that's right.\\n We're dating, so it's not weird\\n to do this kind of thing.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(You're probably just overthinking things.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "T-the sunset looks beautiful, doesn't it?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro's hand, it feels warmer than before...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "H-hey, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "What?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Would you like to take a walk outside tonight?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...At night?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Kokusai dori is close from the hotel, right?\\nAnd there might be other things we'd like to see%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "How about spending some time...just the two of us?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "The two of us...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(The two of us, at night...\\n Futaro, is he perhaps thinking about...!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...No good?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-it's not that I don't want to, but...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oh, well, I mean, if you don't want to,\\nthat's fine. You don't have to push yourself!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(I do want to spend time with him, alone.\\n But if Futaro is really thinking like that%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Eeep!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WOAH?!\\nA-are you okay, Miku?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "S-sorry.\\nI wasn't looking where I was going and tripped.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(My hand feels warm after holding his hand...\\n like his warmth has transferred to me.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "(It's not just his hand. My face also feels hot.\\n It's probably really red... I must look super weird!!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "L-let's hurry!\\nThe sun's going down!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ah!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "WAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Miku?\\nWhat, what's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's n-nothing.\\nI just thought we should hurry before the sun sets.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Wait up?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "What's going on here?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "...Based on Futaro-kun's expression,\\ndid Miku run away again?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 85,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Huh? It seemed like things were going well earlier.\\nWhat happened?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 86,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I have no idea...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 87,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Maybe he tried to make a move,\\nbut it didn't work out?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 88,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Miku...stopped by where Yotsuba and the others are.\\nLet's catch up to her for now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 89,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Yes.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}